         <abstract id="aspace_cc0ba6714e5a8cc02eb9807ea909831e">The records consist of minute books from meetings of the Yale School of Medicine's faculty, its executive board, and the Committee on Examinations, and records of the Board of Permanent Officers.</abstract>
