      <odd id="aspace_44125d9ac810f19fe14edb66bd74bd78">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 27-C (YRG 27-C), Records of officers and faculty of the Yale School of Medicine.</p>  
      </odd>
